<title>
P Position Switch Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove floor console front box. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9806013"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect select lever connector (1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check for continuity between terminals “2” and “7” of select lever connector (2). Replace select lever assembly if defective.
</ptxt>
